• If-None-Match condition evaluates to false, and;
• If-Modified-Since condition evaluates to true;
Then Amazon S3 returns the 304 Not Modified response code. For more information about conditional requests, see RFC 7232. If-None-Match
Return the object only if its entity tag (ETag) is different from the one specified; otherwise,
